  <front>
    <title>The IMAP COMPRESS=DEFLATE extension</title>
    <seriesInfo name="Internet-Draft" value="draft-gulbrandsen-imap-deflate-02"/>
    <author initials="A." surname="Gulbrandsen" fullname="Arnt Gulbrandsen">
      <organization>Oryx Mail Systems GmbH</organization>
    </author>
    <date day="01" month="March" year="2006"/>
    <abstract>
      <t>The COMPRESS=DEFLATE extension allows an IMAP connection to be
    compressed using the DEFLATE algorithm, such that effective
    compression is available even when TLS is used.</t>
    </abstract>
  </front>
</reference>